headline.main: Five Years of the Axis, Coming and Going

lead_paragraph: The word seems to have hung over the world so long, like a bar sinister, that it is difficult to believe that it is only five years ago today that we heard the first mention of the "Axis" as applied to a line of policy connecting Rome and Berlin.
abstract: A O McCormick revs 5 yrs of Axis partnership
